    <item>
      <title>以色列战争目标南移，哈马斯领导成为十字线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/israel-s-war-aims-move-south-with-hamas-leadership-in-crosshairs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[超过100名人质获释。至少 5,000 名哈马斯战士死亡。大约 500 个隧道竖井被毁。以色列军队控制着加沙北部三分之二的地区。距离目标已经完成三分之一了——摧毁哈马斯——并在下一阶段轰炸南方时启动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-03/israel-s-war-aims-move-south-with-hamas-leadership-in-crosshairs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 Dec 2023 17:21:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
